00:00:24.099 --> 00:00:29.880
made a survey for people in their late 20s
as the survey showed right here. Kanazawa showed

00:00:29.880 --> 00:00:36.410
that those with an IQ of over 125 tended to
go to bed at 12:30am and wake up around 8am

00:00:36.410 --> 00:00:43.610
