contribution to when it comes to a person's

00:01:33.030 --> 00:01:36.880
intelligence. The point of the study is that
smarter people can adapt more quickly to changing

00:01:36.880 --> 00:01:42.360
conditions and can sometimes adapt habits
that don't really make sense. While people

00:01:42.360 --> 00:01:47.370
